race.comment: BRAVADO (1) flew the lids with a fast early split last time, hitting the frame with a neck second (16.88) over 300m at this track and making it two placings on end. Can find winning form. BOY (3) had a tough draw to overcome and was game in defeat when only 2 lengths from Barking Blue in second (17.10) at this track. Expected to be in this for a long way. NEW ARRANGEMENT (8) has hit the frame here at the last two runs, most recently finishing third beaten 4 lengths (17.22). Well-placed to take this out. STILTON SWIRL (2) is worth a look over a shorter trip this time.
